242
00:15:25,360 --> 00:15:26,620
Adapun pengiriman pasukan,

243
00:15:26,720 --> 00:15:29,050
Pertama-tama saya harus meminta persetujuan Yang Mulia.

244
00:15:29,070 --> 00:15:30,800
Saya belum bisa memberikan jawaban kepada Anda.

245
00:15:33,150 --> 00:15:34,610
Terima kasih, Yang Mulia.

246
00:15:52,630 --> 00:15:54,360
-Yang Mulia.
-Yang Mulia.

247
00:16:09,080 --> 00:16:09,840
Chu,

248
00:16:11,720 --> 00:16:12,920
